Create ChatRoom
POST /api/chatrooms
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "ChatRoomID": 1,
  "ModuleID": 101,
  "StudentID": 1,
  "Title": "Software Engineering Discussion"
}

Get All ChatRooms
GET /api/chatrooms

Get ChatRoom by ID
GET /api/chatrooms/1

Update ChatRoom
PUT /api/chatrooms/1
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "ModuleID": 101,
  "StudentID": 1,
  "Title": "Updated Software Engineering Discussion"
}

Delete ChatRoom
DELETE /api/chatrooms/1